Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,>> In this session we're going
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to discuss the best practices of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,subscriptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll focus on effectively
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,communicating the value of your
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,subscriptions, streamlining the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,signup flow, and providing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,positive and effortless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lauren, back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laugh ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Subscriptions are the fastest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,growing business model in the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it almost every time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you're ready to sign up for an
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,awesome new service or to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,subscribe to some amazing new
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:00:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,content, this is the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because it's all too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,common for subscriptions to feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,complicated, confusing, or just
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,take too long to sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for a great user experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,make your subscription
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,effortless, transparent, and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,engaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's focus on each of these
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,principles to improve the user
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,experience and design for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription success.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The first step we'll talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,being effortless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So what does it mean for your
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription to be effortless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that people should know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have a subscription.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That way they shouldn't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,look for how to sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's important to be visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out there and don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let people know that you have a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription offer, and ask them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One approach would be to persist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a Subscribe button in your app's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here in "The New York Times"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they do a great job persisting a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Subscribe button.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And they do this tastefully
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the entire UI.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.55,0:02:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's across each article.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is done really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not annoying or pushy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because it families together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,with their interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't present your subscription
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,like a popup add or a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,notification.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because popups and notifications
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,are intended to be dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't want people to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,dismiss your subscription offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Another way to present your
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription would be to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,visible and present it when
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,someone has expressed interest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in a piece of content or in a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,feature that you offer through a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the dating app Her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just say you're swiping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,through a few profiles and you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,accidentally pass on somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,who's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you attempt to rewind that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,profile, and in that moment, the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,app Her tastefully presents an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,option for you to subscribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the rewind feature is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,what they offer as a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an appropriate time for Her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to present you with this offer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because you've shown interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Her does a wonderful job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,presenting the values of your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription right here as well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,with this beautiful, light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So whether you choose to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,persistent in your user
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,interface, or present the option
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to subscribe when someone has
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed interest, make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is visible to people so
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,they know you have a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And no matter what you choose,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,all subscription apps should
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,include a place to sign up in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Settings or Accounts, because
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a very intuitive place for
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,place for people to look to sign
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, to make your subscription
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,effortless, you need to remove
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,friction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Friction is asking for too much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,information, having too many
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,steps, and taking too much time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for somebody to sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do you know when you've
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,asked for too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This data should help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This graph represents a snapshot
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of one month of data from the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,three top video streaming apps
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, while their names have been
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,removed, all the important data
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,here is the clicks to conversion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A subscription flow that has
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,three clicks led to a 61%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,conversion rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And a subscription flow with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,four clicks led to a 48%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,conversion rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, as soon as there was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,nine clicks, it dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,significantly down to 7%.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, while this is just a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,sample, it's clear that you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,should only ask for what is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,absolutely necessary for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because quite literally, less is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Less clicks, less friction, will
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,lead to more conversion and more
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,subscribers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So focus on people on just
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,signing up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like favoriting,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,personalization, and asking for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,additional personal details can
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,all wait until after someone has
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,signed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, by being visible, and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,removing friction, your app
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription will be effortless
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and easier for people to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,subscribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's talk about being
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,transparent with your
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because transparency is the best
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you need to provide clear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,terms so people understand what
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,they're signing up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Strive to be glance-able.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All in one view and in just a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,few seconds, people should be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,able to clearly understand what
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,your subscription offer is and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,how to sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you're making your
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription, always include: a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,concise value proposition, a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,strong call to action, a place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for people to log in if they are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,existing subscribers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Also the ability to restore if
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,someone has a new device.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And a place to sign up that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,includes clear pricing and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And always offer multiple tiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't know if
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody wants to sign up for a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,day, a week, a month, or two
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So try offering three or four
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,different tiers to find out what
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,works best for your audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The MLB At Bat app does a great
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,job and offers all of this in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,one easy-to-understand
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,glance-able view.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is important because
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,most of us are signing up on our
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,By providing clear terms, people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,will be able to make an informed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,decision on how to subscribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved the best for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your app needs to be engaging
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,from the start, before people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,subscribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And the best way to engage them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is through experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them experience your app and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,your app's content before having
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,them subscribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because being able to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and try before you buy is a part
