Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,decisions today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,From trying on clothes to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,attending an open house, or even
